data.description: Welcome to Brookside, one of Shafter's finest neighborhoods. Surrounded by other large, well kept homes, close to the park & local restaurants. This is the place to be! And the home itself has SO much to offer! Built by Wattenbarger, it features a spacious split-wing floor plan with 4 bedrooms, 3 baths. The master suite has a nice soaking tub, shower & large walk-in closet. You'll love the bright open floorplan, tall ceilings, high end tile wood flooring throughout and ample storage. Let's talk about the upgraded chef's kitchen appliances and granite counter tops. Upgraded recess lighting and upgraded impressive country style side gates, New interior paint and has RV parking, 3 car garage and money saving solar panels. Huge backyard the Lot is over a quarter acre and is move in ready, Hurry up and view this home before it's sold.
